00:31.160 --> 00:33.116
Hey, babes.

00:35.600 --> 00:37.670
l've got a presentation at 8:30.

00:37.760 --> 00:40.513
Night-night, darling. Night-night.

00:49.560 --> 00:51.471
Good lad!

01:00.000 --> 01:02.309
Night, darling.

01:11.760 --> 01:13.716
(Baby still cries)
- Sh, sh.

01:26.760 --> 01:28.716
Oh, sod it.

01:29.680 --> 01:31.636
