because my mother...

30:35.000 --> 30:39.710
My sister called me and l don't think my mother
very well, so is it possible to use the phone?

30:39.800 --> 30:41.756
Yes, yes, all right!

30:41.840 --> 30:43.990
You want to give me the key again?

30:44.080 --> 30:46.036
Yes, Ramona.

30:48.840 --> 30:50.796
- Noches.
- Noches.

30:52.160 --> 30:54.116
(Mimics) Noches.

30:57.240 --> 30:59.196
What does she mean, again?

31:02.160 --> 31:03.798
You haven't mentioned the divorce?

31:03.880 --> 31:06.678
- l didn't want to rush it.
- You've been separated seven years!

31:06.760 --> 31:09.433
- lt's hardly indecent haste!
- l will tell him in my own time.

31:09.520 --> 31:10.748
When?

31:10.840 --> 31:12.751
l dunno!

31:12.840 --> 31:15.957
Well, can you give me a clue?
This side of your golden wedding?

31:16.040 --> 31:17.996
Adam, look...

31:19.840 --> 31:22.798
He has had a really rough time recently.

31:22.880 --> 31:25.917
He's been dropped by his record company.
And...

31:26.000 --> 31:28.070
He's got nowhere else to stay,

31:28.160 --> 31:31.152
and...and it's only going to be
for a couple of days,

31:31.240 --> 31:33.993
so you'd just better try and be nice to him.

31:34.080 --> 31:35.991
Are you insane?

31:36.080 --> 31:38.230
Fine. You just get out.

31:38.320 --> 31:40.231
- Me?
- Yes.

31:40.320 --> 31:43.949
You said you wanted to move out
till we got a divorce. Well, then, fine.

31:44.040 --> 31:46.395
l'll ring you at Pete and Jenny's.

31:54.440 --> 31:56.396
Sleep tight, then, mate.

32:01.240 --> 32:03.196
♪ Jimmy, Jimmy!

32:04.040 --> 32:06.952
♪ Jimmy, Jimmy, o-oh

32:07.040 --> 32:08.996
♪ Jimmy, Jimmy!

32:09.840 --> 32:12.877
♪ Poor little Jimmy wouldn't let go

32:12.960 --> 32:14.712
<i>PETE: So where have you been sIeeping?</i>

32:16.560 --> 32:18.471
ln the lounge, on beanbags.

32:18.560 --> 32:20.312
Good job you can sleep anywhere.

32:20.400 --> 32:22.311
Almost anywhere.

32:22.400 --> 32:25.870
- Has Rachel had a word with him yet?
- No, and of course l can't say anything,

32:25.960 --> 32:28.394
though l've tried dropping hints.

32:28.480 --> 32:33.156
(Over backing track) ♪ Our D-l-V-O-R-C-E

32:33.240 --> 32:37.153
♪ Becomes final today

32:37.240 --> 32:39.196
(Turns stereo off)

32:41.440 --> 32:43.590
<i>He's been with us three days.</i>

32:43.680 --> 32:45.989
How can she not have mentioned it?

32:46.080 --> 32:49.117
- What could they possibly be talking about?
- No, not too close.

32:49.200 --> 32:52.795
Keep the grip a hand's length away
from the old man.

