33:58.440 --> 34:00.396
l'm ready.

34:01.080 --> 34:03.594
<i>DAVlD: You reaIIy don't Iike him, do you?</i>

34:03.680 --> 34:07.992
What bugs me most is that he's so...perfect.

34:09.040 --> 34:10.951
First of all, he's fit.

34:11.040 --> 34:12.951
Do you want a hand with that?

34:13.040 --> 34:14.996
l can manage.

34:16.639 --> 34:18.471
Second, he's...

34:20.000 --> 34:22.992
<i>..the gaIIoping...frigging gourmet.</i>

34:26.440 --> 34:28.556
lt should be ready in about 20.

34:33.440 --> 34:35.351
Excellent.

34:35.440 --> 34:38.512
And third,
just to make me feel like a total plank...

34:38.600 --> 34:40.556
(Gentle, melodic strumming)

34:41.440 --> 34:45.228
<i>..he's become Didsbury's answer
to John bIoody Denver.</i>

34:45.320 --> 34:49.154
♪ You only get one chance in life

34:49.239 --> 34:52.357
♪ Well, l didn't make it known

34:52.440 --> 34:56.149
♪ You only get one chance at love

34:56.239 --> 34:59.357
♪ Well, l didn't take it, yeah

34:59.440 --> 35:05.959
♪ lf l could, l know exactly
what l'd say to you tonight

35:06.040 --> 35:12.354
♪ Oh, if l could, l wouldn't let you walk away

35:12.440 --> 35:14.749
♪ Come what may...

35:14.840 --> 35:16.796
(TV blares)

35:18.280 --> 35:20.191
All in all...

35:20.280 --> 35:22.191
he's everything l'm not.

35:22.280 --> 35:24.350
lncluding married to Rachel.

35:24.440 --> 35:27.557
Excuse me, do you have a calculator, please?

35:35.840 --> 35:37.353
(Sighs)

35:38.240 --> 35:39.355
Jen,

35:39.440 --> 35:41.396
say something to me.

